00:01:03.572 --> 00:01:05.664
(Yongxiu Palace)

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:15.480
Congratulations on regaining favor.

00:01:16.080 --> 00:01:17.080
I'm glad you're back.

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:18.800
For involving you in what happened,

00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:20.760
I feel deeply sorry.

00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:24.080
To serve Your Highness again
is my blessing.

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:29.440
From now on, don't rush
to do menial tasks

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:30.800
like serving tea.

00:01:31.640 --> 00:01:33.800
Let those lazy maids handle some chores.

00:01:34.080 --> 00:01:35.104
Yes.

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:36.520
Your Ladyship,

00:01:36.520 --> 00:01:39.320
recently many servants
in our palace have fallen ill.

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:41.680
The staff has become inadequate,

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:43.680
so duties are being performed slower.

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:45.152
They're ill?

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:48.280
Perhaps due to recent weather change.

00:01:48.880 --> 00:01:50.680
I retrieved medicine
from the Medical Bureau.

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:54.760
When most of the people
in the palace fall sick,

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:55.880
it's weird.

00:01:56.560 --> 00:01:58.280
Inquire in other places

00:01:58.280 --> 00:01:59.680
to detect any abnormalities.

00:02:31.760 --> 00:02:33.320
It seems you're not infected.

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:35.120
Why are you here?

00:02:36.520 --> 00:02:37.840
Smallpox is rampaging the palace,

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:38.720
spreading panic.

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:41.000
With lax security here,

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:42.240
I snuck in.

00:02:42.600 --> 00:02:43.840
Protect yourself.

00:02:44.440 --> 00:02:45.600
Don't come here.

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:50.400
After all, I owe you all this.

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:52.200
Don't worry.

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:53.640
I'll get you out of the palace.

00:02:54.040 --> 00:02:55.168
There's no need.

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:57.280
Tend to your own affairs.

00:02:57.640 --> 00:02:59.520
As a descendant of the former dynasty,

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:02.640
helping you is my honor.

00:03:04.880 --> 00:03:05.840
I don't understand.

00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:08.360
Since you're aware
of your special identity,

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:09.960
why did you

00:03:10.280 --> 00:03:11.840
act so recklessly?

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.600
In one's lifetime,

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:17.160
we simply do things we enjoy.

00:03:18.480 --> 00:03:19.880
No deeper reasons exist.

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:22.640
Now that you've done what you wanted,

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:25.640
you should leave the palace
to live well.

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:27.040
Don't act rashly.

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:29.640
Helping you escape once
was miracle enough.

00:03:30.520 --> 00:03:31.720
Don't stir up more trouble.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:37.600
I'll ensure your safety.

00:03:37.856 --> 00:03:38.840
Wait for my news.

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:39.776
I don't need it!

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:42.960
My life exists solely for my master.

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:44.480
Dying for my master

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:46.520
would be a worthy death.

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:50.440
No one's life

00:03:50.880 --> 00:03:52.400
is predetermined at birth.

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:55.280
Your life should belong to yourself.

00:03:55.552 --> 00:03:56.640
Blindly sacrificing it

00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:57.800
for me,

00:03:57.800 --> 00:03:59.400
for personal gain, or for anyone else

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:00.400
is never worthwhile.

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:02.592
Don't be constrained.

00:04:03.320 --> 00:04:04.320
Be your true self.

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:06.960
Seek your own purpose in life.

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:10.320
I've never contemplated

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:12.520
what you said before,

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:15.840
nor will I consider it henceforth.

00:04:20.400 --> 00:04:21.240
Trust me.

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:23.640
I will get you out of here.

00:04:36.680 --> 00:04:38.280
May Your Majesty be ever blessed.

00:04:38.640 --> 00:04:39.744
Concubine Yun,

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:40.736
don't approach.

00:04:40.920 --> 00:04:41.840
Your Majesty,

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:43.240
with smallpox rampaging the palace,

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:45.040
to protect your health,

00:04:46.200 --> 00:04:47.440
I propose

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:50.040
retreating to the summer palace
temporarily.

00:04:50.040 --> 00:04:51.072
I'm fine.

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:52.736
Return to your palace.

00:04:57.600 --> 00:04:58.520
Someone!

00:04:58.520 --> 00:04:59.424
Summon the physicians!

00:05:04.608 --> 00:05:05.536
Your Majesty,

00:05:05.536 --> 00:05:06.440
