00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:08.992
Chief Physician Zhang,

00:05:09.200 --> 00:05:10.520
treat His Majesty immediately.

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:12.000
Rest assured.

00:05:12.320 --> 00:05:13.680
I will exert every effort

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:15.640
to cure His Majesty.

