00:05:40.440 --> 00:05:41.760
Return now and start packing.

00:05:42.440 --> 00:05:43.560
I'll fetch Noble Lady Mu.

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:44.440
Okay.

00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:45.472
Be extremely careful.

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:47.240
