00:07:28.840 --> 00:07:30.240
What's past is past.

00:07:30.880 --> 00:07:31.776
And you

00:07:31.960 --> 00:07:33.600
have already paid the price.

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.456
I

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:36.896
don't hate you.

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:42.592
Ling Yun,

00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:44.560
