00:07:48.480 --> 00:07:49.720
Find a chance to leave here

00:07:50.440 --> 00:07:52.240
and live your own life.

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:54.464
Your Highness,

00:07:54.840 --> 00:07:56.640
with smallpox raging
through the palace now,

00:07:56.640 --> 00:07:57.520
