00:07:57.520 --> 00:07:59.840
Let's find a way to escape
and take shelter outside.

00:08:00.840 --> 00:08:02.240
After all that's happened,

00:08:03.240 --> 00:08:04.480
I finally see things clearly.

00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:06.208
You were right.

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:07.800
